--- Requires Installation:
* ncursesw development library (For example on Ubuntu: sudo apt install libncursesw5-dev)
* pkg-config
* automake
* autoconf
* binutils
* ncurses
* glibc
* make
* gcc

--- Make sure charset is set to UTF-8
run the 'locale' command

--- Spell
autoreconf -iv && ./configure && sudo make install

--- File Structure
/usr/local/bin/typp
